Angular --->is a framework

difference b/w library and framework ... is library is single functioned and framework is a sructured way (frontend , backend sab kuch ho) ...library sy ap tor tor k apna ghar (website )bnaskty ho i.e: guestroom k liye alg library , kitchen k liye alg etc.

phly react k sath jab next js ni thy to wo just library thy yani frontend(client) side py hi work krskty thy and jab nextjs ai to framework bngya q k nextjs framework h so ye server side py v work krskty.



yad rkhna...node js ek framework h aur framework me frontend backend both hoty.















